Seasoned actor Bohang Moeko has revealed his latest role in BET's upcoming telenovela Isono. He will play the character of Gabriel. He describes the character as a mysterious guy, who has his own demons. "Meet Gabriel, son of Mother Mary. On the surface he appears to be this perfect and doting son but looks can be deceiving. Find out what Gabriel is hiding when Isono premiers on BET Africa Channel 129 on the 27th of July Mon-Fri 21:30 CAT," he wrote. The actor has in other roles shown his versatility, even as gay Tshepo in Scandal and Mojalefa in Isidingo. The show is scheduled to premier next month. SEE POST BELOW: 